bpp/descriptor.long_desc: Discover the best places to eat, shop and hang out around you. Earn rewards by uploading all your bills.

descriptor.name: Kullad Cafe
descriptor.long_desc: A great place to hangout with a group of friends, it is a very pocket-friendly cafe popular amongst the youngsters. It has a cool ambience with great music and is famous for its coffee and tea served in mud cup, delicious Parathas, crunchy Sandwiches, Rolls, Cool shakes, juices and chillers. If you ever plan on taking a lazy day off, then you can even have their amazing and pocket-friendly dishes home delivered.

descriptor.name: Veg Cheese Grilled Sandwich
descriptor.short_desc: Serves 1 | Sandwich grilled with round slices of cucumber, onions, tomatoes, dressed with mayonaise, some pinch of black pepper and topped with grated cheese. Grilled in butter.
descriptor.long_desc: Serves 1 | Sandwich grilled with round slices of cucumber, onions, tomatoes, dressed with mayonaise, some pinch of black pepper and topped with grated cheese. Grilled in butter.

descriptor.name: Poha
descriptor.short_desc: Homestyle poha prepared with crispyness of peanut and served with namkeen and lemon. Traditional north indian breakfast.
descriptor.long_desc: Homestyle poha prepared with crispyness of peanut and served with namkeen and lemon. Traditional north indian breakfast.

descriptor.name: Ginger Tea
descriptor.short_desc: Tea made with strong tea leaves in steaming milk using fresh ginger. Chai which keeps you going whole day warm and fresh.(2 cup ginger tea).
descriptor.long_desc: Tea made with strong tea leaves in steaming milk using fresh ginger. Chai which keeps you going whole day warm and fresh.(2 cup ginger tea).

descriptor.name: Aloo Paratha
descriptor.short_desc: Whole wheat paratha stuffed with mashed potato and pinch of all Indian spices. Served with curd & green chutney.
descriptor.long_desc: Whole wheat paratha stuffed with mashed potato and pinch of all Indian spices. Served with curd & green chutney.

descriptor.name: Icebreakers And Go Italia
descriptor.long_desc: Icebreakers HSR If you can not resist pampering yourselves with some sweet treats, Icebreakers in HSR is where you should be headed to. The sinful yet indulgent offerings will have you hooked up from the very first look. One bite into it and you will know why it remains to be a popular establishment for all dessert lovers out there! descriptor.name: Food Affair, Pure Veg
descriptor.long_desc: Food Affair, Pure Veg is a F&B-Casual Dining outlet that offers a wide variety of delicious and healthy vegetarian dishes. The restaurant has a cozy and inviting atmosphere, perfect for a casual lunch or dinner. The menu features a variety of North Indian, South Indian, Chinese, and Continental dishes. The restaurant also offers a variety of beverages, including juices, shakes, and mocktails. The staff is friendly and attentive, and the prices are reasonable. Food Affair, Pure Veg is the perfect place to enjoy a delicious and healthy meal with friends and family.
